
Help on: skaven

Skaven are a small rat-like folk. They are very nimble,
sneaky and untrustworthy. While they aren't very intelligent,
they posess a kind of cunning which allows them to quickly
adapt to new situations.

               Physical:         Mental:

    Strength:  average           poor
Constitution:  average           hopeless
   Dexterity:  excellent         average
    Charisma:  poor              pathetic
